Late Afro Pop legend and musical genius Robbie Malinga’s Instagram followers were surprised to see his account active with posts of flashy cars. What they were initially not aware of is that his son, Robbie Malinga Jr (17), had taken over his late father’s verified Instagram account and posting on it. One of the posts on the account that caught many people’s attention was a video that has since gone viral in which Robbie Jr can be seen revving a stationary Porsche before hopping out and introducing himself to his dad’s followers. "If you don't know me, now you know me, it’s Robbie Jnr aka Rob Mali. I'm moving in now, it's verified boys, you know what the f**k going on…, “he said in the video. The video left many amused and got a lot of people talking on Twitter.  